OL,3,CGrandmother saw bruise on toddler's
OL,4,Cback days before death, murder trial
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FKris Jepson reports from Teesside
OL,8,FCrown Court.
OL,10,FThe grandmother of a toddler who was
OL,11,Fallegedly murdered asked "what the
OL,12,Fhell" when she saw a bruise on the
OL,13,Fgirl's back days before her death, a
OL,14,Fcourt heard.
OL,16,FIsabelle Welsh, two, collapsed at her
OL,17,Fhome in Hartington Close, Thornaby,
OL,18,FTeesside, having suffered a "massive
OL,19,Fhead injury" and could not be saved,
OL,20,Fjurors were told.
OL,26,@sD@ZOUtD@EO]zD@]OU{D@LO]
